// http://www.stateair.net/web/post/1/5.html
val udfQuality = udf[String, Int](v => v match {
    case v if (v <  0)   => "No Data"
    case v if (v <= 50 ) => "Health"
    case v if (v <= 100) => "Moderate"
    case v if (v <= 150) => "Unhealthy for Sensitive Groups"
    case v if (v <= 200) => "Unhealthy"
    case v if (v <= 300) => "Very Unhealthy"
    case v if (v <= 500) => "Hazardous"
    case v if (v > 500) => "Beyond Index"
})
val udfQualityIndex = udf[String, Int](v => v match {
    case v if (v <  0)   => "-1"
    case v if (v <= 50 ) => "0"
    case v if (v <= 100) => "1"
    case v if (v <= 150) => "2"
    case v if (v <= 200) => "3"
    case v if (v <= 300) => "4"
    case v if (v <= 500) => "5"
    case v if (v > 500) => "6"
})
import java.util.GregorianCalendar
import java.util.Calendar
val udfWeekDay = udf[Int, Int, Int, Int, Int]((year, month, day, hour) => new GregorianCalendar(year, month, day, hour, 0).get(Calendar.DAY_OF_WEEK))

val hasValues = original.filter($"value" > 0)

val enriched = hasValues.withColumn("quality", udfQuality($"value")).
   withColumn("qualityIndex", udfQualityIndex($"value")).
   withColumn("weekDay", udfWeekDay($"year", $"month", $"day", $"hour")).
   withColumn("yearMonth", $"year" * 100 + $"month").
   withColumn("yearMonthDay", $"year" * 10000 + $"month" * 100 + $"day").
   withColumn("monthDay", $"month" * 100 + $"day").
   withColumn("weekHour", $"weekDay" * 100 + $"hour")
enriched.registerTempTable("enriched")
enriched.take(1)
def getQuartile(cols: String*) = {
    val groupCols = cols.mkString(",")
    val sql = s"""select $groupCols, 
                    PERCENTILE(value, 0.25) as q1, 
                    PERCENTILE(value, 0.85) as q3, 
                    PERCENTILE(value, 0.5) as median,  
                    max(value) as high, 
                    min(value) as low 
                  from enriched group by $groupCols"""
    sqlContext.sql(sql)
}
